  "text": "Office of the Registrar\nThe Registrar's Office supports teaching and learning at NYU Shanghai by maintaining the integrity of academic policies and the student information system. It is the steward of NYU Shanghai's student records from application to degree conferral in perpetuity.\nThe Office of the Registrar provides NYU Shanghai students with the following services:\nTranscripts\nVerification Documents\nAlbert\nDegree and Graduation\nAcademic Calendar\nRegistration Guidelines\nGrading Information\nPrivacy of Student Records\nStudent Forms\nContact Us\nLocation: Suite N928, North Hall, 567 Yangsi West Road, Pudong Shanghai, China 200124\nRegistrar: Winnie Wilson\nEmail:shanghai.registrar@nyu.edu\nPhone: 021-2059-5750",
